      "name": "Hydraulic performance validation — pressure-flow curve comparison",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pressure rise versus flow rate compared against experimental measurements at 5 operating points (2500–3500 RPM, 2–6 L/min). Mean absolute error 4.2% across all operating points. Uncertainty quantification performed via Latin hypercube sampling over inlet boundary conditions.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/morrison-uq-001-hydraulic-lhs"
