      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Velocity field validation — PIV comparison at mid-plane",
      "description": "CFD velocity magnitude contours compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements at the impeller mid-plane under 3000 RPM / 4 L/min reference condition. Spatial agreement assessed via normalized root-mean-square deviation (NRMSD = 6.8%). Aleatory uncertainty arising from inter-run PIV variability and pump manufacturing tolerances was assessed qualitatively by the experimental team; structured probabilistic UQ characterization was not performed for this result, as the investigators noted that inherent variability was assessed qualitatively through repeat-run scatter bands rather than through a formal uncertainty propagation framework.",
      "hasMetric": "https://uofa.net/synth/metric/morrison-nrmsd-velocity"
