    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all 5 COU operating points. Grid convergence index within acceptance threshold. Validation activities conducted at COU-representative conditions. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
